title: Guy Richie Movies
description:
Guy Richie Movies here, including Lock, Stock, and 2 Smoking Barrels (1998), Snatch (2000), Swept Away (2002), Revolver (2006), and RocknRolla (2008).

One of my most favorite movies of all time is Revolver.  I also liked Lock, Stock, and Two Smoking Barrels and RocknRolla.  And while I did like Snatch, I probably preferred it the least of the four.  I haven't even seen Swept Away, I've heard it's horrible though.
